snippet.title: Keep Keepers - Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In Keep Keepers Tower Defense meets Base Management. Strategically place a variety of defenses. Craft wacky ammunition like fiery peppers and boomerang bananas. Discover amazing weapons and automate your economy while defending against waves of enemies. Can you handle the chaos? Play Solo or Co-op.

Wishlist on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2354330/?utm_source=yt

Join us on our Discord server and play the Keep Keepers Demo now:
 https://discord.gg/n24hXgwhaW
